Title: Flows and Duality Symmetries in N=1 Supersymmetric Gauge Theories

Authors: O. Aharony, J. Sonnenschein and S. Yankielowicz

Comments: 31 pages, uses harvmac.tex and tables.tex

Minor changes - version accepted to Nucl. Phys. BJournal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B449 (1995) 509-534

We present more examples of dual N=1 SUSY gauge theories. This set oftheories is connected by flows to both Seiberg's and Kutasov's dual theories.This provides a unifying picture of the various dual theories. We investigatethe dual theories, their flat directions and mass perturbations.